### Combat Synergies

**Whirlwind Strike + Aggressive Stance:** Hit all adjacent enemies, generate massive Momentum from multiple hits, enable follow-up techniques.

**Perfect Parry + Defensive Stance:** Already generating Momentum when attacked, Perfect Parry ensures survival against overwhelming threats.

